   "source": [
    "# Overview\n",
    "- This dataset contains **5,000 e-commerce transactions** from a Turkish online retail platform, spanning from January 2023 to March 2024 where each row represents one unique customer purchase.\n",
    "- The objective is to analyze monthly performance trends, customer engagement behavior and segmentation patterns to identify revenue drivers and business improvement opportunities.\n",
    "- This dataset is cited from Kaggle titled \"E-Commerce Customer Behavior and Sales Dataset (2024) Turkish Online Retail Platform Data (2023-2024), Available from Kaggle.\""
   ]
  },
