  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b2da8f31",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "####  In 2023, total orders had major spikes in March, May, August, October and December, with notable drops in April, September and November. This pattern could reflect seasonal promotions or holiday shopping periods.\n",
    "#### In 2024, total orders steadily declined in the first three months, indicating a slower start compared to the previous year."
   ]
  },
